    Class                       Purpose
    table                       for absic styling
    table-striped               for striped table
    table-bordered              for table with borders on all sides of the table and cells
    table-hover                 to highlight the row on hover
    table-condensed             to make tables more compact by cutting cell padding in half
    table-responsive            makes table responsive by displaying a horizontal scrollbar on small devices (under 768px)

